  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0ba8\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc8\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb2\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Maithiri will discuss Sri Lanka's economic crisis with the heads of state in the Philippines",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former President Maithripala Sirisena has gone to the Philippines to attend the 'International Leadership Conference - 2022', where he will discuss Sri Lanka's economic crisis during a meeting with the heads of state of other countries.",
        "Former President Maithripala Sirisena is in the Philippines to attend the 'International Leadership Conference 2022' in Manila, Philippines.",
        "He left the country early on the 29th of Friday through a Singapore Airlines flight.",
        "The 'International Leadership Conference 2022' will be held on 30th and 31st. About 28 countries will be represented in this conference, including heads of state and members of parliament.",
        "It is considered a rare opportunity for Sri Lanka that Sri Lanka's sixth Executive President Maithripala Sirisena has been given the opportunity to deliver the opening speech at this conference in which many major countries are participating.",
        "Former President Maithripala Sirisena has said that he is looking forward to meeting many foreign leaders at this international conference in which important world leaders will participate.",
        "Former President Maithripala Sirisena has mentioned that he will focus on the support available from abroad for the current economic crisis in Sri Lanka."
      ],
